    "title": "Ny orientering om maksimal timeløn i offentligt løntilskud pr. 1. april 2012",
    "documentTypeId": "200",
    "isSagsforlobPeriodValid": true,
    "shortName": "SKR nr 9200 af 25/04/2012",
    "documentHtml": "<div class=\"bjelke\">Den fulde tekst</div><p class=\"Titel2\">Ny orientering om maksimal timeløn i offentligt løntilskud pr. 1. april 2012</p>\r\n<p class=\"Tekst\">Til jobcentre, a-kasser, beskæftigelsesregionerne, beskæftigelsesankenævnene, Ankestyrelsen, Beskæftigelsesrådet, Danske Regioner, Moderniseringsstyrelsen, DA, LO og KL</p>\r\n<p class=\"Tekst\">Arbejdsmarkedsstyrelsen har konstateret, at der beklageligvis er sket en beregningsteknisk fejl i forbindelse med styrelsens skrivelse af 27. marts 2012 om den maksimale timeløn pr. 1. april 2012.</p>\r\n<p class=\"Tekst\">Den maksimale timeløn udgør pr. 1. april 2012 <span class=\"Bold\">114,66 kr.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"Tekst\">Skrivelsen af 27. marts 2012 bortfalder. Satsen på 114,66 kr. gælder for løn for perioden fra 1. april 2012.</p>\r\n<p class=\"Tekst\">For fuldtidsforsikrede dagpengemodtagere, der er berettiget til den højeste dagpengesats på 788 kr. om dagen, fremgår løn- og arbejdstid af nedenstående eksempel:</p>\r\n<p>\r\n   <div style=\"width:100%\">\r\n      <table class=\"Containertable\" style=\"border-style: none; border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px;\">\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border-style: none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n               <table valign=\"top\" class=\"Maintable\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\" width=\"680\">\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"381\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"140\"> </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"381\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Højeste dagpengesats pr. uge:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">(5 x 788)</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"140\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">3.940,00 kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"381\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Reguleret med 8 % AM-bidrag:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">(3.940 : 0,92)</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"140\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">4.282,61 kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"381\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Timeløn pr. 1. april 2012:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"140\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">114,66 kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"381\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Antal timer pr. uge:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">(4.282,61: 114,66 kr.)</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"140\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">37,35 timer</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"381\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Antal timer pr. uge oprundes til</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"140\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">38 timer</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"381\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Ugeløn:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">(38 x 114,66 kr.)</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"140\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">4.357,08 kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"381\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Arbejdstid i løntilskud:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 0pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"140\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">37 timer.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"381\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt solid #000000;border-right: 0pt solid #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 0pt solid #000000;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"140\"> </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n               </table>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Tekst\">Der beregnes løn for 38 timer. Arbejdstiden i løntilskudsjobbet kan dog ikke overstige den almindelige ugentlige arbejdstid på 37 timer, jf. § 60, stk. 1, i bekendtgørelse om en aktiv beskæftigelsesindsats.</p><div class=\"Givet\" id=\"Givet\"><p class=\"Givet\" align=\"center\">Arbejdsmarkedsstyrelsen, den 25. april 2012</p><p class=\"Sign1\" align=\"center\">Morten Gatzwiller<br />Chefkonsulent</p><p class=\"Sign2\" align=\"right\"></p></div>",
